formation.\",\"level\":\"MEDIUM\"}],\"short_answer_questions\":[{\"question\":\"How can ASHA workers track immunization schedules effectively?\",\"short_answer\":\"By maintaining updated immunization records and using reminder systems for upcoming vaccination dates.\",\"explanation\":\"Accurate record-keeping and reminders ensure timely vaccinations, crucial for maintaining high immunization rates.\",\"level\":\"MEDIUM\"}]}},{\"number\":\"10/10\",\"main_question\":\"A new health initiative requires ASHA workers to integrate digital tools in their daily tasks. What challenges might they face, and how can these be addressed?\",\"sub_question\":{\"multiple_correct_questions\":[{\"question\":\"Which challenges do ASHA workers face when implementing digital tools?\",\"choices\":[\"Lack of digital literacy\",\"Inadequate internet connectivity\",\"Resistance to change\",\"Insufficient training programs\"],\"correct_answer_text_list\":[\"Lack of digital literacy\",\"Inadequate internet connectivity\",\"Insufficient training programs\"],\"explanation\":\"ASHA workers may struggle with digital literacy, connectivity issues, and lack of sufficient training, all of which can hinder the effective use of digital tools.\",\"level\":\"DIFFICULT\"}],\"short_answer_questions\":[{\"question\":\"What support can be provided to ASHA workers to enhance their use of digital tools?\",\"short_answer\":\"Provide comprehensive training programs and supply necessary digital resources to improve proficiency and accessibility.\",\"explanation\":\"Training and resources are essential to enable ASHA workers to effectively integrate digital tools into their tasks, improving efficiency and service delivery.\",\"level\":\"DIFFICULT\"}]}}]}', '2025-04-11 16:14:07.185426'),
