(1, 1, NULL, 1, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Easy', 'What is the primary purpose of a URL?', 'What is the primary purpose of a URL?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"To locate resources on the internet\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"To encrypt data\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"To serve as a form of authentication\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"To manage cookies\"}]}', '{\"id\": 1}', NULL, 'URLs are used to specify the addresses of resources on the internet.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:16.958407', '2025-04-01 21:01:16.958407'),
(2, 1, NULL, 2, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Medium', 'Which component of a URL specifies the protocol used for communication?', 'Which component of a URL specifies the protocol used for communication?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Host\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Path\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Scheme\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Fragment\"}]}', '{\"id\": 3}', NULL, 'The scheme component of a URL specifies the protocol, such as HTTP or HTTPS.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:16.971407', '2025-04-01 21:01:16.971407'),
(3, 1, NULL, 3, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Difficult', 'In the context of URLs, what does IDN stand for?', 'In the context of URLs, what does IDN stand for?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"International Domain Name\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Internet Domain Name\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Internal Domain Network\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Internationalized Domain Names\"}]}', '{\"id\": 4}', NULL, 'IDN refers to domains that include characters from different scripts, such as Arabic or Cyrillic.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:16.977406', '2025-04-01 21:01:16.977406'),
(4, 1, NULL, 4, 'CHECKBOXES', 'Easy', 'Which of the following are considered reserved characters in a URL?', 'Which of the following are considered reserved characters in a URL?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"?\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"&\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"/\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"#\"}]}', '{\"ids\": [1, 2]}', NULL, 'Reserved characters in URLs have special meanings and include characters like \'?\' and \'&\'.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:16.995406', '2025-04-01 21:01:16.995406'),
(5, 1, NULL, 5, 'CHECKBOXES', 'Medium', 'What are common practices to secure URLs against attacks?', 'What are common practices to secure URLs against attacks?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Use HTTPS\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Implement input validation\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Ignore query parameters\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Utilize URL encoding\"}]}', '{\"ids\": [1, 2, 4]}', NULL, 'Securing URLs involves using HTTPS, validating inputs, and encoding URLs to prevent attacks.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.002406', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.002406'),
(6, 1, NULL, 6, 'TEXTBOX', 'Medium', 'Explain the difference between a URL and a URI.', 'Explain the difference between a URL and a URI.', NULL, '{\"answer\": \"A URL is a specific type of URI that provides a means to locate a resource on the internet, while a URI can be a name, locator, or both.\"}', NULL, 'URIs are a broader category that includes URLs and URNs. URLs specify locations.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.007406', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.007406'),
(7, 1, NULL, 7, 'TEXTBOX', 'Difficult', 'Describe the role of canonicalization in SEO.', 'Describe the role of canonicalization in SEO.', NULL, '{\"answer\": \"Canonicalization helps in preventing duplicate content issues by specifying a preferred URL for indexing by search engines.\"}', NULL, 'Canonicalization tells search engines which version of a URL to index when there are multiple URLs for the same content.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.009406', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.009406'),
(8, 1, NULL, 8, 'TEXTAREA', 'Medium', 'Discuss the impact of URL shortening services on user privacy and security.', 'Discuss the impact of URL shortening services on user privacy and security.', NULL, '{\"answer\": \"URL shortening services can obscure the destination URL, leading to potential privacy and security risks as users cannot easily verify the target site before clicking. These services also introduce a dependency on third-party services, which could track user interactions or become unavailable, breaking the links.\"}', 'Consider how URL shortening can affect the visibility of the destination and the potential for misuse.', 'URL shortening can hide the actual URL, making it difficult to verify destinations, thus posing privacy and security challenges.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.013405', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.013405'),
(9, 1, NULL, 9, 'TEXTAREA', 'Difficult', 'Explain how URL routing can be optimized for performance in web applications.', 'Explain how URL routing can be optimized for performance in web applications.', NULL, '{\"answer\": \"Optimizing URL routing involves minimizing the complexity of routes, leveraging caching mechanisms, and using efficient algorithms to resolve URL patterns. This can reduce server load and improve response times, enhancing user experience.\"}', 'Think about how route complexity and caching can impact performance.', 'Efficient URL routing reduces server processing time and optimizes resource utilization.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.039409', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.039409'),
(10, 1, NULL, 10, 'FILL_BLANKS', 'Easy', 'A URL\'s [___] is used to separate the domain name from the specific resource path.', 'A URL\'s [___] is used to separate the domain name from the specific resource path.', '{\"items\": [{\"id\": 1}]}', '{\"answers\": [{\"id\": 1, \"answer\": \"path\"}]}', NULL, 'The path follows the domain in a URL and specifies the resource location.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.042406', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.042406'),
(11, 1, NULL, 11, 'FILL_BLANKS', 'Medium', 'In a URL, the [___] character is used to separate the query parameters from the rest of the URL.', 'In a URL, the [___] character is used to separate the query parameters from the rest of the URL.', '{\"items\": [{\"id\": 1}]}', '{\"answers\": [{\"id\": 1, \"answer\": \"?\"}]}', NULL, 'The \'?\' character indicates the beginning of the query string in a URL.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.047428', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.047428'),
(12, 1, NULL, 12, 'TRUE_FALSE', 'Easy', 'HTTP and HTTPS are interchangeable as they both perform the same function.', 'HTTP and HTTPS are interchangeable as they both perform the same function.', '{\"trueLabel\": \"True\", \"falseLabel\": \"False\"}', '{\"value\": false}', NULL, 'HTTP and HTTPS are not interchangeable; HTTPS provides a secure layer over HTTP using SSL/TLS encryption.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.052409', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.052409'),
(13, 1, NULL, 13, 'PAIR_MATCH', 'Difficult', 'Match the URL component with its function.', 'Match the URL component with its function.', '{\"items\": [{\"id\": 1, \"colAText\": \"Path\", \"colBText\": \"Specifies the protocol\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"colAText\": \"Scheme\", \"colBText\": \"Identifies the domain\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"colAText\": \"Host\", \"colBText\": \"References a secondary resource within the primary resource\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"colAText\": \"Fragment\", \"colBText\": \"Locates the resource\"}]}', '{\"answers\": [{\"id\": 1, \"correctId\": 4}, {\"id\": 2, \"correctId\": 1}, {\"id\": 3, \"correctId\": 2}, {\"id\": 4, \"correctId\": 3}]}', NULL, 'Each URL component has a specific role in defining the resource\'s location and access method.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.055406', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.055406'),
(14, 1, NULL, 14, 'GROUP_QUESTION', NULL, 'Analyze the implications of using internationalized domain names (IDNs) in global e-commerce platforms.', 'Analyze the implications of using internationalized domain names (IDNs) in global e-commerce platforms.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.062408', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.062408'),
(15, 1, NULL, 15, 'GROUP_QUESTION', NULL, 'Evaluate the role of URL structures in RESTful API design.', 'Evaluate the role of URL structures in RESTful API design.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.065409', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.065409'),
(16, 1, 15, 1, 'CHECKBOXES', 'Difficult', 'Which principles are important for RESTful URL design?', 'Which principles are important for RESTful URL design?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Statelessness\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Use of HTTP methods\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Client-server architecture\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Nested resources\"}]}', '{\"ids\": [1, 2, 4]}', NULL, 'RESTful design emphasizes clear, stateless URLs that utilize HTTP methods effectively.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.068520', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.095415'),
(17, 1, 15, 2, 'TEXTBOX', 'Difficult', 'Why is it important to have a consistent URL structure in APIs?', 'Why is it important to have a consistent URL structure in APIs?', NULL, '{\"answer\": \"Consistent URL structures ensure clarity, predictability, and easier maintenance of APIs.\"}', NULL, 'Consistency in URL structures helps developers understand and predict API behavior, improving usability and maintenance.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.075411', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.096413'),
(18, 1, 14, 1, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Medium', 'What is one major benefit of using IDNs for businesses?', 'What is one major benefit of using IDNs for businesses?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Improved security\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Broader market reach\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Simplified URL structure\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Enhanced SEO\"}]}', '{\"id\": 2}', NULL, 'IDNs allow businesses to reach non-English speaking markets by using native language domains.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.078408', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.096413'),
(19, 1, 14, 2, 'TEXTAREA', 'Medium', 'Discuss the potential challenges e-commerce platforms might face when implementing IDNs.', 'Discuss the potential challenges e-commerce platforms might face when implementing IDNs.', NULL, '{\"answer\": \"Challenges include increased complexity in managing domain names, potential security issues with homograph attacks, and ensuring consistent user experience across different languages and scripts.\"}', 'Consider technical, security, and user experience aspects.', 'IDNs introduce complexity and security challenges, which need to be managed carefully.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-01 21:01:17.080408', '2025-04-01 21:01:17.096413'),
(20, 2, NULL, 1, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Difficult', 'What is the primary investment risk difference between Defined Benefit (DB) and Defined Contribution (DC) plans?', 'What is the primary investment risk difference between Defined Benefit (DB) and Defined Contribution (DC) plans?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Employer bears the risk in DB, employee bears the risk in DC\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Employer and employee share the risk equally in both\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Employee bears the risk in DB, employer bears the risk in DC\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"No investment risk in either plan\"}]}', '{\"id\": 1}', NULL, 'In Defined Benefit plans, the employer is responsible for providing the specified retirement benefit and bears the investment risk. In Defined Contribution plans, the employee\'s account balance depends on contributions and investment returns, thus the employee bears the risk.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-02 11:01:15.063484', '2025-04-02 11:01:15.063484'),
(21, 2, NULL, 2, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Difficult', 'What is the maximum service requirement a 401(k) plan can impose for eligibility under ERISA guidelines?', 'What is the maximum service requirement a 401(k) plan can impose for eligibility under ERISA guidelines?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Six months\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"One year\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Two years\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"No requirement\"}]}', '{\"id\": 2}', NULL, 'ERISA allows a maximum one-year service requirement for eligibility in a 401(k) plan, although plans can choose to require less. This helps to balance between encouraging employee retention and providing retirement benefits.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-02 11:01:15.090485', '2025-04-02 11:01:15.090485'),
(22, 2, NULL, 3, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Difficult', 'Under ERISA, what is the vesting requirement for employer contributions if a plan uses a graded vesting schedule?', 'Under ERISA, what is the vesting requirement for employer contributions if a plan uses a graded vesting schedule?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"100% after 3 years\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"20% after 2 years, 40% after 3 years, 60% after 4 years, 80% after 5 years, 100% after 6 years\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Immediate 100% vesting\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"50% vested after 5 years\"}]}', '{\"id\": 2}', NULL, 'ERISA requires a participant to be fully vested over a six-year period under a graded vesting schedule, with incremental vesting starting after two years of service.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-02 11:01:15.096499', '2025-04-02 11:01:15.096499'),
