(69, 8, NULL, 1, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Easy', 'What is the primary difference between a defined benefit plan and a defined contribution plan?', 'What is the primary difference between a defined benefit plan and a defined contribution plan?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Defined benefit plan has a definite benefit formula, defined contribution plan does not\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Defined contribution plan guarantees a fixed return, defined benefit plan does not\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Defined benefit plan is more flexible, defined contribution plan is less flexible\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Defined contribution plan is only for highly compensated employees\"}]}', '{\"id\": 1}', NULL, 'In defined benefit plans, the benefit is calculated based on a formula, whereas in defined contribution plans, the final benefit depends on contributions and investment returns.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-16 11:46:48.085129', '2025-04-16 11:46:48.085129'),
