(71, 8, NULL, 3, 'MULTIPLE_CHOICE', 'Difficult', 'What is required to ensure non-discrimination in qualified plans under ERISA?', 'What is required to ensure non-discrimination in qualified plans under ERISA?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Plans must include all employees regardless of compensation\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Plans may not favor highly compensated employees\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Plans must offer the same contributions to all employees\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Plans must exclude part-time employees\"}]}', '{\"id\": 2}', NULL, 'ERISA guidelines ensure that no particular group, such as highly compensated employees, is favored in qualified plans.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-16 11:46:48.143130', '2025-04-16 11:46:48.143130'),
(72, 8, NULL, 4, 'CHECKBOXES', 'Easy', 'Under which conditions can employees participate in a 401(k) plan?', 'Under which conditions can employees participate in a 401(k) plan?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Employee must be over 21 years old\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Employee must have completed one year of service\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Employee must work full-time\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Employee must be a permanent employee\"}]}', '{\"ids\": [1, 2]}', NULL, 'Eligibility is often based on age and service, allowing participation once employees are over 21 and have completed a year of service.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-16 11:46:48.146132', '2025-04-16 11:46:48.146132'),
(73, 8, NULL, 5, 'CHECKBOXES', 'Medium', 'What are the key features of a 401(k) plan?', 'What are the key features of a 401(k) plan?', '{\"choices\": [{\"id\": 1, \"text\": \"Allows employee contributions\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"text\": \"Provides tax-deferred growth\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"text\": \"Employer contributions are mandatory\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"text\": \"Requires vesting schedule for all contributions\"}]}', '{\"ids\": [1, 2]}', NULL, '401(k) plans allow employees to contribute and grow their retirement savings tax-deferred. Employer contributions are not mandatory, and vesting applies to employer contributions.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-16 11:46:48.150132', '2025-04-16 11:46:48.150132'),
(74, 8, NULL, 6, 'TEXTBOX', 'Easy', 'What is a cliff vesting schedule?', 'What is a cliff vesting schedule?', NULL, '{\"answer\": \"A cliff vesting schedule is one where participants are fully vested after a certain period, with no partial vesting before that time.\"}', NULL, 'In cliff vesting, employees gain full ownership of employer contributions after a specified period, like three years, with no partial vesting before that.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-16 11:46:48.153132', '2025-04-16 11:46:48.153132'),
(75, 8, NULL, 7, 'FILL_BLANKS', 'Medium', 'In a 401(k) plan, [___] contributions reduce the participant\'s current taxable income.', 'In a 401(k) plan, [___] contributions reduce the participant\'s current taxable income.', '{\"items\": [{\"id\": 1}]}', '{\"answers\": [{\"id\": 1, \"answer\": \"before-tax\"}]}', NULL, 'Before-tax contributions are deducted from gross income before taxes, reducing taxable income.', 1.00, NULL, 0, '2025-04-16 11:46:48.155131', '2025-04-16 11:46:48.155131'),
